Introduction

The SUSO Method is not just designed for marketers who want to take their SEO skill set to the next level, but also for entrepreneurs, CEOs, CTOs, tech savvy computer scientists and developers, data analysts and intelligent marketers who want to know the ins and outs of Google’s Algorithm.

Read more

1. Wonders of the World Wide Web

Becoming a successful SEO requires an understanding of how the World Wide Web webs. In this module, we will discuss how the Internet works before taking a closer look at the three core phases of search engines: crawling, indexing and ranking before concluding with a brief look at how other search engines compare to Google.

Read more

Advanced SEO for ambitious marketers

There are countless SEO guides around, many of which simply tell you how to be a good SEO.

But if you approach organic search from Google’s perspective, rather than how an SEO thinks, you’ll be at a huge advantage.

The learning materials in our guide are created for marketers who want to gain deep, technical knowledge of Google’s algorithm, to fuel their strategic SEO decisions.

If you want to gain an upper hand in SEO wisdom – register your interest today for SUSO’s free Advanced SEO Textbook today.

Practical knowledge

We’ve also included practical tasks for you to complete throughout the course, not to mention the quiz at the end of every module!
